scripts.cy:smoke:dev: npx cypress run "TAGS=@smoke" --env ENV="dev" --spec cypress\integration\sparks\SmokeTests.spec.js --browser chrome --headed --reporter mocha-allure-reporter
scripts.cy:smoke:stage: npx cypress run --env ENV="stage" --spec cypress\integration\sparks\SmokeTests.spec.js --browser chrome --headed --reporter mocha-allure-reporter
scripts.cy:smoke:prod: npx cypress run --env ENV="prod" --spec cypress\integration\sparks\SmokeTests.spec.js --browser chrome --headed --reporter mocha-allure-reporter
scripts.cy:regression:set1:dev: npx cypress run "TAGS=@regression" --env ENV="dev" --spec cypress\integration\sparks\T1NewProject.spec.js --browser chrome --headed --reporter mocha-allure-reporter

scripts.cy:stage: npm run delete:reportFolder && npx cypress run --env ENV="stage" --spec cypress\integration\sparks\SmokeTests.spec.js --browser chrome --headed
scripts.cy:production: npm run delete:reportFolder && npx cypress run --env ENV="production" --spec cypress\integration\sparks\SmokeTests.spec.js --browser chrome --headed
scripts.test:cli: npm run delete:reportFolder && cypress run --spec cypress\integration\sparks\SmokeTests.spec.js --browser chrome --headed
scripts.create:html:report: npm run merge:reports && marge --reporter-options --timestamp --reportDir TestReport cypress-combined-report.json
